Uses of Package
nl.tno.sensorstorm.api.processing

  • Packages that use nl.tno.sensorstorm.api.processing 
    Package Description
    nl.tno.sensorstorm.api.processing
    This package contains interfaces for components that can process DataParticels (Fetchers, Batchers and Operations) and MetaParticles (MetaParticleHandler).
    nl.tno.sensorstorm.gracefullshutdown
    This package contains the gracefull shutdown functionality.
    nl.tno.sensorstorm.impl
    This package contains classes are used internally for SensorStorm.
    nl.tno.sensorstorm.storm
    This package contains classes that can be used in storm: the SensorStormSpout, the SensorStormBolt and the custom Stream groupings.
    nl.tno.sensorstorm.timer
    This package contains the timer ffunctionality.

    Class and Description
    BatcherException
    Special type of Exception for when an error occurs in the batching process.
    Operation
    An operation performs the processing of particles in a fieldGroupValue.
    OperationException
    Special type of Exception for when an error occurs in the Operation.

  • Classes in nl.tno.sensorstorm.api.processing used by nl.tno.sensorstorm.impl 
    Class and Description
    Batcher
    An interface describing the batch functionality: to collect one or more particles in a batch based on a certain criteria.
    Operation
    An operation performs the processing of particles in a fieldGroupValue.
    ParticleBatchOperation
    A ParticleBatchOperation performs the processing of particles in a channel, particles will be grouped by a Batcher into a list.
    SingleParticleOperation
    A SingleParticleOperation performs the processing of particles in a channel, each particle will be presented to this operation one by one.
